quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"Mong`a rona! Re lumela ho seo u se senotseng, e bile re latela Moromuoa eo U mo romeletseng. Ka hona re ngole har’a ba jereng bopaki ba ‘nete.”"
  3,54,"Ba ithera, ‘Allah le Eena U ile A ithera khahlanong le bona: Moreri ea phahametseng bohle ke Allah"
  3,55,"Hopola nakong eo Allah a neng a re: “Oho jesu! Ke tla U nka ke u nyollele ho ‘Na, Ke hlakole ho uena liketseletso tsa bahana-tumelo; Ke tla matlafatsa ba o latelang ka ho phahamela bahana-tumelo ho fihlela mohla letsatsi la tsoho. Ruri poelo ea lona bohle e ho ‘na, ke tla ahlola lipakeng tsa lona ho seo se bakileng likhang"
  3,56,Haele botlhoka-tumelo bona ke tla ba otla ka kotlo e boima lefats’eng lena le ho bo-tlang; ebile ba ke ke ba eba le bathusi.”
  3,57,"Haele ba kholoang bona ba bile ba etsa mesebetsi e hloekileng, Ruri Allah U tla lefa meputso ea bona ka botlalo. Allah ha a rate baetsa-liphoso"
  3,58,Ruri sena seo re le phetelang sona ke ts’enolo le temoso e chorileng
  3,59,"Ruri! Papiso ea Jesu kapel’a Allah e ts’oana le’a Adama. O ‘mopile ka lerole, eaba O re ho eena “eba!” eaba o ba teng"
  3,60,"Ena ke ‘nete e tsoang ho Mong`a hau, ka hona u se ke oa ba e mong oa ba belaelang"
  3,61,"Haeba ho ka ba le ba u phehisang khang ka eena, ka mor’a hoba tsebo e honyelle ho uena, u re ho bona: “tlohong! Re tla bokella bara ba rona le ba lona, le basali ba rona le basali ba lona ‘moho, e be rona le lona; e be re rapela Mong`a rona ‘moho ka boikokobetso le ka tieo re kope thohako ea Allah holim’a ba leshano.”"